PrediqaFraudIQ — Technical Stack (India Deployment)
Executive Summary
PrediqaFraudIQ is built on a cloud-native, microservices architecture optimized for Indian regulatory requirements (data localization, IRDAI compliance, Ind-AS 117 / IFRS 17 audit trails). The stack is battle-tested from the US deployment and re-architected for Indian insurance ecosystem integration.

Core Technology Stack
1. Data Ingestion Layer

2. AI/ML Detection Engine

3. Clinical Cross-Match Engine (India-Adapted)

4. Data Storage & Processing

5. Identity & Security Stack

6. Integration Layer

7. DevOps & Infrastructure


